---
/**
 * Redesigned Shift Section
 */
---

<section class="shift section-pad">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="reveal">With Vedic Meditation, something shifts.</h2>
        <div class="shift-grid">
            <div class="shift-pair reveal">
                <p class="from">Deep rest happens</p>
                <p class="to">Stress leaves the body</p>
            </div>
            <div class="shift-pair reveal">
                <p class="from">Natural rhythm returns</p>
                <p class="to">Life flows again</p>
            </div>
            <div class="shift-pair reveal">
                <p class="from">Thoughts lose urgency</p>
                <p class="to">Thinking gains clarity</p>
            </div>
            <div class="shift-pair reveal">
                <p class="from">Less becomes more</p>
                <p class="to">Being becomes easy</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="shift-bottom reveal">
            <h3>Become the version of you that feels more like you.</h3>
            <p>
                The one who smiles more easily, rests more deeply and moves
                through life with greater ease.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .shift {
        background: linear-gradient(
            180deg,
            var(--color-indigo) 0%,
            #253840 100%
        );
        color: var(--color-warm-white);
        text-align: center;
    }
    .shift h2 {
        font-size: clamp(26px, 3vw, 36px);
        font-style: italic;
        margin-bottom: 64px;
        color: var(--color-warm-white);
    }
    .shift-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        gap: 40px;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto 80px;
    }
    .shift-pair {
        position: relative;
    }
    .shift-pair .from {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: rgba(244, 242, 238, 0.45);
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .shift-pair .to {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--color-golden-seed);
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-style: italic;
    }
    .shift-bottom {
        max-width: 580px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .shift-bottom h3 {
        font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);
        font-style: italic;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .shift-bottom p {
        color: rgba(244, 242, 238, 0.7);
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.9;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .shift-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .shift-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 32px;
        }
    }
</style>
